    6              / THIS PROGRAM IS USED TO PATCH AN RK05 OR OLD SERIAL DISK IMAGE BY THE
    7              / SERVER ON INITIAL BOOT.  THE ONLY DIFFERENCES FROM CONSYS.PA ARE THE
    8              / HANDLER HEADER AND ENTRY POINT ADDRESS FOR THE SECOND DEVICE.
