   33              /BOOT CODE
   34              
   35 00031  7731          BTWC-BLAST      /TWO'S COMP OF LENGTH OF BOOT CODE FOR BUILD
   36              
   37                      RELOC 0
   38 00000* 7400  BTWC,   -0400           /WORD COUNT TO TRANSFER 
   39 00001* 0001  BTCA,   0001            /CURRENT ADDRESS TO STORE WORD.
   40 00002* 0000  BTTMP,  .-.             /THIS IS AN INITIAL DONT CARE VALUE.
   41              
   42              / THE NEXT FOUR WORDS REPLACE THE PATCH CODE IN THE BOOT2 HELP LOADER
   43 00003* 7605  OS8GO,  7605            /OS8 ENTRY POINT
   44 00004* 0047  BTSRC,  0047
   45 00005* 7647  BTDST1, 7647
   46 00006* 7600  BTDST2, 7600
   47              
   48 00007* 6031  BOOT2,  KSF             /GET A CHARACTER FROM SERIAL DISK SERVER
   49 00010* 5007          JMP .-1
   50 00011* 6036          KRB
   51 00012* 7006          RTL             /LEFT SHIFT 4 BITS TO BUILD UPPER HALF
   52 00013* 7006          RTL
   53 00014* 3002          DCA BTTMP       /SAVE FOR COMBINE
   54 00015* 6031          KSF             /GET LOWER 6 BITS
   55 00016* 5015          JMP .-1
   56 00017* 6036          KRB
   57 00020* 1002          TAD BTTMP
   58 00021* 3401          DCA I BTCA      /STORE THE WORD IN MEMORY
   59 00022* 2001          ISZ BTCA        /POINT AT NEXT ADDRESS
   60 00023* 2000          ISZ BTWC        /SKIP IF DONE
   61 00024* 5007          JMP BOOT2       /GO DO THE NEXT WORD
   62              
   63              / WHEN WE GET HERE THE BOOT BLOCK IS LOADED IN MEM PAGES 0 AND 1
   64              / WE NOW NEED TO COPY THEM INTO PLACE.
   65              
   66              / FIRST DO THE FIELD 1 PIECE
   67 00025* 1404  BTCPY1, TAD I BTSRC     /LOAD
   68 00026* 6211          CDF 10          /SWITCH TO FIELD 1
   69 00027* 3405          DCA I BTDST1    /STORE
   70 00030* 6201          CDF 00          /SWITCH TO FIELD 0
   71 00031* 2004          ISZ BTSRC       /BUMP SRC ADDRESS WILL NEVER SKIP
   72 00032* 2005          ISZ BTDST1      /BUMP DST ADDRESS AND SKIP IF DONE
   73 00033* 5025          JMP BTCPY1
   74              
   75              / NEXT DO THE FIELD 0 PIECE
   76 00034* 1404  BTCPY2, TAD I BTSRC     /LOAD
   77 00035* 3406          DCA I BTDST2    /STORE
   78 00036* 2004          ISZ BTSRC       /BUMP SRC ADDRESS WILL NEVER SKIP
   79 00037* 2006          ISZ BTDST2      /BUMP DST ADDRESS AND SKIP IF DONE



